observations.recommendation:
We recommended that Management instruct the Municipal Accountant to:

prepare the necessary Journal Entries to correct the understatement of Depreciation Expense for 2023 and Accumulated Depreciation as of the same year;

coordinate with the GSO to determine the appropriate useful lives of the PPEs with no estimated useful lives and date of acquisition, after that provide for the appropriate deprecation;

reconcile with the GSO on the beginning balances included in the schedule of depreciation considered as unidentified/inexistent/unreconciled and determine the correctness of the provided depreciation for these unidentified/inexistent/unreconciled PPEs based on available data; and

Judiciously review the Schedule of Depreciation and determine the discrepancies with the financial statements to ensure accuracy and consistency in reporting under IPSASs 1 and 17.

